Tutorial
Nice, now the line cannot pass through all the points, but
it tries to be as close to all of them as possible.

Sometimes you want to add a point that will be very far
away from the origin. To do that you need to either scroll
the mouse to change the scale or dragged the mouse
to move the camera. In this case You will move the camera by
dragging the mouse. Just press the left mouse button
and move the mouse. Let's add the last point which will be very high.
Follow the arrows!